1) setup pip, virtualenv (sudo pip install virtualenv)
2) create a virtual env  using virtualenv myapp.
3) goto folder of virtual env  and activate using "source bin/activate"
4) pip install Django==1.10  (to check pip is installed use pip freeze)


Creating a django project:

1) django admin.py startproject
2) python manage.py migrate (aaplying chnages to the database)
3) create superuser  (python manage.py createsuperuser)
4) python manage.py runserver (running an application server)

